title: Monday Pt2: Statement wins in week-8; Top NFC teams; Nate Burleson
itunes:title: Monday Pt2: Statement wins in week-8; Top NFC teams; Nate Burleson
description:
Part Two of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty sharing which team earned their statement win of the week. They also weigh in on where the Minnesota Vikings stack up in the NFC and then they’re joined by Nate Burleson. Part two of the GMFB podcast finishes up handing out game balls in the form of halloween candy.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
